Developer Terms of Use
des: The Texas Children’s Urgent Care skill can provide helpful information about the wait times and hours at our 10+ locations across Houston and Austin. Enable the skill by saying “Alexa, open Texas Children's Urgent Care”. Once enabled, you can ask about patient wait times at the location nearest you (wait times are subject to change) as well as find out the hours we are open.
